  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The addition of dexamethasone (DxaM) to local anesthetic may significantly prolong the
      duration of a block in total knee arthroplasty. The aim of this study is to determine whether
      this is a systemic or local effect.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
